release.changelog:
Hello to the brand-new update!
* Added support for Android 16 OS.
* Added 6-month and annual subscription plans to the subscriptions page.
* Optimized performance for low-memory devices.
* Fixed some bugs.
* Added new bugs we haven't discovered yet :)
